Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:07.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servant Saber 应召唤而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:10.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的Master吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:16.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:20.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为事出突然而有些混乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:25.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是眼前的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她无法形容的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加的魔术师为七人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:42.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们Master役使分为七个职阶的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围绕独一无二的圣杯互相厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:54.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝身寄于吾侧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾命系于吾剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣服于圣杯之本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:05.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,循此意 循此理则应之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃永世为善之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃永世作恶之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝 三大言灵护体之七天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由抑止之轮降临于此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:27.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天平的守护者！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:35.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:51.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被一个不得了的Master抽中了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:01.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然时间还早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但前辈居然会睡过头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我似乎在修理这家伙时睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:11.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:17.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在我看来 前辈偶尔睡过两次比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好让我照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很慢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样娇惯士郎 小心他得寸进尺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里是娇惯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看前辈累了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤姐才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准了早晚吃饭的时候过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不叫得寸进尺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:46.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在士郎长大成人之前 我要代替你父母照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对切嗣这样发过誓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要每天来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:54.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱 你做的味增汤味道绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有前辈教我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我听着点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:06.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要批卷子呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:07.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤村老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎精神特别足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天瓦斯泄漏事件的受害人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在仍神志不清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:23.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在新都经常发生瓦斯泄漏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多半是配线短路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换条新的就能过冬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我要集中精神修理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你离开一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好细致的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不会妨碍卫宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 细致是细致…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的做法非同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两条电热丝快断掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能撑一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电源线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用绝缘胶带应该能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候老爸说过来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:26.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我联想和把握物体构造的能力很强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为魔术师的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:36.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎为零
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了 一成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:54.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看上了那个远坂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫看上了远坂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级A班 远坂凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容貌端庄 头脑明晰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何负面传言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是几乎所有男生的憧憬对象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:32.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想不通 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为按士郎所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要拯救所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:51.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味着放弃另一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:59.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在我能理解老爸的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:03.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无辜的人们要遭受不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:11.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么努力 能得救的还是寥寥无几
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救不了所有人是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:16.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫君真能干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天连其他人的份都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:33.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是没有拒绝过别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能叫了不起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:42.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点召唤出来 会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:28.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你还在啊 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:46.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真闲 这个时候还在闲逛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:52.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是应一成的要求 去学生会修东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍学生会的马屁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:58.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这边的杂活也能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们弓道场也乱的很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:04.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙啊 从前就特别喜欢助人为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:32.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方似乎在等日落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要攻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚天气不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的小哥也这样想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能看到Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 果然是Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小姐您知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以视为我的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着陆拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器是枪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:25.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你名为Lancer的Servant吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:32.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的Servant似乎不是正面单挑类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 既然碰上了就要打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 怎么办 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:50.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让我看看你的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区弓兵居然想学剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:01.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是操场那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:14.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有人没走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:31.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑的还蛮远的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫杀人灭口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会产生牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对此不是早有觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我为你送终吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:15.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:18.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪造破损的脏器代用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时修复心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:35.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:37.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有实体 还互相残杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差点被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 心脏遇刺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:23.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我被在场的某人救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:29.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 我在意的是你为什么要那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的战斗不能被人察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要马上灭口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:43.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancer也是 比起和我们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先选择了消灭目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:54.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他迟早会发觉到目击者还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:56.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目击者要是还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancer是不会坐视不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:06.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:08.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:09.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 反正已经倒霉到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只能前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同调 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:20.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构成材质 补强完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:22.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会像刚才那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:35.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 一天之内居然要两次杀死同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不要迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:48.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得被刺穿心脏还能活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很微弱 但能感觉到魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这是自找苦吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我蛮吃惊的 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 你就是第七个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:31.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好容易才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会轻易赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:43.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样毫无意义的死去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:51.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:07.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servant Saber 应召唤而来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的Master吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servant Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以往 我的剑与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命运和我与共
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至此 契约完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目不可视的剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:59.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 一味防守有负枪兵之名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可先出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我先问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:14.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是斧 是枪 不 或许是弓也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说了 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心脏 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.47,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,665)\fs35}Gáe Bolg
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺穿死棘之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:35.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 刚才的是因果倒转吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:39.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你躲过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,665)\fs35}Gáe Bolg
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的必杀 刺穿死棘之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:43.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺穿死棘之枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是爱尔兰的光之御子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:50.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然使出了这一招 不能一招必杀就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太有名也不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:56.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 是名为Saber的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:09.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer 消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:38.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子怎么能乱挥武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况你受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人就在眼前 我不能撤剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名鼎鼎的Servant Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会违抗主人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:53.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 卫宫君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被卷进了一场竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:08.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为圣杯战争的七名魔术师的厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监督就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言峰教会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有资格得到圣杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拥有Servant的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你们七个战至最后一人时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣杯会出现在胜者的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:28.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:30.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为被选出的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:34.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有意参加这场圣杯战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:41.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:46.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说十年前的火灾因圣杯而起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能让那种事情再度上演
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望终于要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有明确的恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:04.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望就无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:07.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义需要与之对立的邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:09.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:16.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最崇高的愿望和最丑恶的念头意义相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必掩饰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:23.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你内心的纠葛作为人类十分正常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:27.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就还了你的人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:29.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂你真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:32.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算给我戴高帽 我也不会手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:33.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:42.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:44.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第二次见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:46.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 这家伙强太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:54.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉亚苏菲尔‧冯‧艾因兹贝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:55.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说你就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾因兹贝伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:23:01.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒暄就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:03.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们都要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:04.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:09.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:10.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:23.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:33.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:41.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:23:59.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:02.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们根本不可能赢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:04.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Berserker啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:07.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是希腊最强的英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:09.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希腊最强的英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:11.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:14.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会再生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:16.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把她的头割下来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:21.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.55,0:24:38.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 这样太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.93,0:24:39.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:47.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.21,0:24:50.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面时 我会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.08,0:24:59.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:21.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 刚刚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:29.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸色似乎不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.09,0:25:34.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.51,0:25:36.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.04,0:25:37.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.21,0:25:39.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨晚一事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.37,0:25:40.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.35,0:25:41.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.55,0:25:45.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为Master 那种举动让我很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.24,0:25:49.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗交给我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.80,0:25:52.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎请完成自己的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.68,0:25:55.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为Master的你不需要保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:57.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有这样做的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.61,0:26:01.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护一个女孩子 需要什么理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.34,0:26:06.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.40,0:26:08.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.36,0:26:11.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.63,0:26:18.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种酥软的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.89,0:26:27.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.41,0:26:39.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫君
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.57,0:26:43.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己有多愚蠢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.83,0:26:45.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.68,0:26:48.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master居然不带Servant到处闲晃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.12,0:26:51.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像是在引颈就戮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.96,0:26:55.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不仅让人无语 甚至让我很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.72,0:26:59.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 什么杀不杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.42,0:27:01.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗不是要避人耳目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.93,0:27:03.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的校园…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.55,0:27:06.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但现在这里有旁人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.64,0:27:15.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以逃 但只会增加自己的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.98,0:27:17.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正赢的肯定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.54,0:27:19.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.14,0:27:21.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是学校
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:23.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还有人留在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.29,0:27:26.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.40,0:27:31.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会放过眼前的机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.18,0:27:35.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北欧魔术里有gandr射击这种咒术 你听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.52,0:27:41.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得是用指尖指人 让对方生病…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.04,0:27:44.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.65,0:27:46.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会取你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.21,0:27:47.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.89,0:27:52.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂 刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.30,0:28:08.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫君…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:11.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胳膊 你的胳膊上开了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.26,0:28:14.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂 那孩子拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.97,0:28:15.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫君
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.03,0:28:18.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里没错
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.12,0:28:42.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫君 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.51,0:28:54.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在所布的结界一旦发动
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.43,0:28:57.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会溶解吸收结界内的人的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.70,0:28:59.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性质简直坏到极点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.52,0:29:01.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是不惜一切代价
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.06,0:29:05.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想增强自己的Servant吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.89,0:29:08.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那个Servant 就是昨天战斗过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.28,0:29:11.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.17,0:29:15.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有确凿证据 但这样想最为自然
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.20,0:29:21.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但不能确定他是Master
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:22.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.35,0:29:25.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.82,0:29:30.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在只能延迟结界的发动
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.48,0:29:32.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.49,0:29:35.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要找出咒刻
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.31,0:29:38.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照卫宫君的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.18,0:29:41.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是感觉不对劲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.10,0:29:43.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气腥甜的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.18,0:29:45.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.29,0:29:47.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.20,0:29:51.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 要是这么容易找到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.60,0:29:52.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用费力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.88,0:29:54.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 也要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.25,0:29:55.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动员全副神经
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.50,0:29:56.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个一个找…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.85,0:29:58.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.50,0:30:06.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消去 摘除手术 第二节
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.26,0:30:10.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消去 摘除手术 第二节
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.53,0:30:19.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是 咒刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.38,0:30:19.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.50,0:30:23.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能有寻找这种东西的才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.76,0:30:26.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.82,0:30:28.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫君 放学后留下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.04,0:30:32.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来让那个暗中活动的Master大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.65,0:30:37.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:40.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 几乎没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.62,0:30:41.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:43.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.21,0:30:49.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方万万想不到这么多咒刻会在一天内被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.43,0:30:51.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有所行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.26,0:30:54.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住对方马脚的好机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.50,0:30:55.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.89,0:30:58.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.08,0:31:01.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我费这么大劲
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.53,0:31:02.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要请你赎罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.93,0:31:05.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫君
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.98,0:31:08.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.66,0:31:10.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能到处逛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.04,0:31:15.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你担心了吗 远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.42,0:31:16.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.93,0:31:18.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定合作了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.68,0:31:21.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是被干掉 我的计划会被打乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.83,0:31:22.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.28,0:31:24.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 哼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.70,0:31:35.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这、个感觉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.17,0:31:51.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是确认一下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.91,0:32:15.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.49,0:32:26.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 快通知远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.50,0:32:29.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.51,0:32:39.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用掉好吗 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.77,0:32:41.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.74,0:32:45.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.13,0:32:55.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫已经两年没来过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.96,0:32:56.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.59,0:33:00.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让她陪在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.51,0:33:02.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也害怕你的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.70,0:33:05.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上让我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.96,0:33:07.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己却是这副德行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.07,0:33:10.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 进入正题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.17,0:33:13.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和我联手吗 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.48,0:33:20.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然成为了Master 但我还不太习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.90,0:33:23.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找个信得过的人合作
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.87,0:33:26.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么成为Master的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.61,0:33:29.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间桐是魔术师世家
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.35,0:33:31.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.75,0:33:34.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 血脉却已经枯竭了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.12,0:33:37.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我们不是魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.87,0:33:39.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只学过知识
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.96,0:33:42.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非樱也学了魔术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.20,0:33:44.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.36,0:33:46.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是孩子有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.79,0:33:48.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承家业的只有长子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.27,0:33:53.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被选为继承人的孩子会一无所知的长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.59,0:33:56.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常会被送给别家做养子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.04,0:34:00.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 樱和圣杯战争无关是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.26,0:34:03.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法使用魔术 你没有知识
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.21,0:34:05.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.23,0:34:08.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们携手对付眼前的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.06,0:34:11.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂凛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.47,0:34:13.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.70,0:34:16.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.55,0:34:17.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.49,0:34:20.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然早晚要和远坂交手
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.96,0:34:23.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在值得信赖 我也想相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.12,0:34:25.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.54,0:34:27.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也会暂时旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.24,0:34:30.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉帮不上你的忙 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.54,0:34:35.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 为了表示友好 我告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.23,0:34:37.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.79,0:34:40.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一个Master盘踞在柳洞寺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.56,0:34:43.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳洞寺？ 一成家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.30,0:34:45.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我的Servant说
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.04,0:34:48.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山上潜伏着魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.19,0:34:50.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正大量收集灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.66,0:34:51.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.84,0:34:53.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算亲自动手
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.93,0:34:57.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集灵魂的… 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.96,0:35:05.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.39,0:35:07.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.99,0:35:10.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只会死在其他Master手里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.62,0:35:39.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.42,0:35:44.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为Assassin的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.55,0:35:46.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木小十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.28,0:36:14.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 胸口好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.27,0:36:16.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.89,0:36:18.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.62,0:36:23.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.51,0:36:26.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.03,0:36:31.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不容我留后手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.59,0:36:35.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于要认真起来了吗 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.83,0:36:45.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一击 你能接下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.69,0:36:47.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assassin的Servant！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.64,0:36:58.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.78,0:37:06.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该称之为台风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.91,0:37:08.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但应该不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.60,0:37:14.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其深处的东西 让我见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.13,0:37:16.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.78,0:37:25.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.00,0:37:37.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.60,0:37:40.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人企图觊觎你的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.58,0:37:44.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 就不光是你我二人的单挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.71,0:37:49.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你不想分个胜负吗 Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.85,0:37:54.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时有人搅局对你来说不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.99,0:37:58.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 接你的人也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.34,0:38:03.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偷窥之人把目标换成小鬼之前
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.84,0:38:05.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.72,0:38:08.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.76,0:38:09.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.38,0:38:14.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.92,0:38:25.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.24,0:38:41.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 与其让你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.97,0:38:43.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我自己战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.80,0:38:46.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎的护卫 和一层纸没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.76,0:38:50.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在小看Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.29,0:38:52.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一介凡人居然想打倒英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.53,0:38:54.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.56,0:38:59.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙只是不想让你受伤罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.99,0:39:00.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.04,0:39:02.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.80,0:39:03.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.08,0:39:05.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让Saber受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.37,0:39:08.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以明知不行也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.92,0:39:11.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管明知赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.83,0:39:12.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要争胜
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.79,0:39:16.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算结果会害死自己也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.83,0:39:22.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起自己 那家伙更关心别人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.69,0:39:31.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.40,0:39:34.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意你参加战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.74,0:39:37.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我也有我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.35,0:39:39.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎要体验一次
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.20,0:39:43.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不只是一次 只要时间允许
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.91,0:39:46.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要体验死这一战斗结果
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.91,0:39:48.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以熟悉战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.84,0:39:51.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.59,0:39:55.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诫过自己不要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.24,0:39:59.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只打了两个小时就举手投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.01,0:40:03.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不需要感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:07.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎的刺击里没有杂念 很有力道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.51,0:40:11.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接点水
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.73,0:40:12.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.07,0:40:19.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.63,0:40:22.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.40,0:40:24.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.03,0:40:28.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 Saber之所以帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.89,0:40:30.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了取得圣杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.09,0:40:34.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber你 为什么需要圣杯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.43,0:40:37.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以需要圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.54,0:40:39.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了达成我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.17,0:40:44.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.67,0:40:46.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想从头来过
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.66,0:40:53.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.31,0:40:56.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 卫宫 看你今天也没来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.58,0:40:58.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.80,0:41:00.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.94,0:41:04.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 作为有同样烦恼的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.27,0:41:06.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你单独谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.32,0:41:07.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.85,0:41:10.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 不要告诉远坂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.69,0:41:12.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.15,0:41:21.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 现在应该是休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.12,0:41:25.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.26,0:41:47.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说敌人来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.75,0:41:49.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.76,0:41:53.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比预想中还有精神 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.86,0:41:56.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个点子你还满意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.81,0:41:59.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你干的吗 慎二！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.42,0:42:00.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.79,0:42:03.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.67,0:42:05.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就马上发动了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.03,0:42:09.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 你知道自己在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.56,0:42:11.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想命令我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.08,0:42:16.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我住手的话 就该跪下求我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.30,0:42:21.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后通告 停止结界 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.40,0:42:26.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么不爽的话 就动手试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.67,0:42:27.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.30,0:42:30.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.32,0:42:39.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好耶 Rider不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.65,0:42:49.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外 我的兵刃杀不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.30,0:42:48.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你磨蹭什么呢 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.03,0:42:51.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 快点杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.96,0:42:58.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.91,0:43:04.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.25,0:43:08.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空说明了 你明白情况吧 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.17,0:43:12.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 士郎 先给你包扎伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.87,0:43:14.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.55,0:43:16.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只有你才能打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.61,0:43:17.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.93,0:43:19.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须阻止结界
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.48,0:43:21.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤姐和同学们有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.08,0:43:23.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意的话 我就用令咒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.73,0:43:26.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.39,0:43:29.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请指示 Master
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.93,0:43:46.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.55,0:43:48.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider由我打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.81,0:43:50.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去对付Rider的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.57,0:43:51.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.41,0:43:53.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你不快点收拾卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.04,0:43:55.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.61,0:44:08.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider 你干什么呢 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.68,0:44:12.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厉害 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.27,0:44:16.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.03,0:44:21.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止结界 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.42,0:44:22.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.65,0:44:25.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 是我输了 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.48,0:44:27.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上停止结界
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.77,0:44:29.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.11,0:44:32.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止鲜血神殿 马上！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.37,0:44:46.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.76,0:44:48.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二 舍弃你的令咒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.87,0:44:51.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不用再争斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.73,0:44:53.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.96,0:44:55.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.27,0:44:57.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失去令咒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.71,0:44:59.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没法控制Rider了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.23,0:45:01.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.74,0:45:03.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去言峰教会就好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.70,0:45:06.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出战斗的Master 他会负责保护
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.60,0:45:15.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.11,0:45:22.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.60,0:45:24.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.76,0:45:26.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 退下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.77,0:45:30.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider企图解放维持结界所用的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.60,0:45:47.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.13,0:45:48.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider想使用宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.65,0:46:15.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她所说的 只把宝具用于脱身了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.98,0:46:16.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.66,0:46:18.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.12,0:46:32.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.37,0:46:41.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.01,0:46:45.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想对你说的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.24,0:46:48.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下我擅自回应敌人的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.75,0:46:50.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图自己战斗一事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.70,0:46:53.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾自己安危一事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.68,0:46:55.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.39,0:46:57.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何一项都是足以害死你的愚蠢行为
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.61,0:47:01.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样把我逼上绝路 有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.78,0:47:02.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.99,0:47:07.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你一定要给我说个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.40,0:47:09.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.92,0:47:12.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.78,0:47:15.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把力量借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.59,0:47:18.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只凭我一人 是赢不过其他Master的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.69,0:47:21.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.13,0:47:23.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深切体会到了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.61,0:47:29.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你承认先前的作法是错误的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.21,0:47:32.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不认为那是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.28,0:47:36.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是现在 我也不想看到Saber受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.73,0:47:38.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber若要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.34,0:47:39.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.93,0:47:41.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.81,0:47:43.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有这一点不能让步
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.60,0:47:47.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Saber独自战斗这种事 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.87,0:47:55.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份顽固 真符合你的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.47,0:47:59.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今也不需要回答了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.34,0:48:02.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.35,0:48:05.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有谁比我更愿意帮你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.20,0:48:16.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.20,0:48:20.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.12,0:48:24.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是瞒着我开作战会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.87,0:48:26.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.91,0:48:31.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在给Master把脉 确认他是否健康
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.09,0:48:34.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好奇怪的把脉方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.37,0:48:36.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.66,0:48:38.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.00,0:48:39.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.32,0:48:40.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber的备用衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.28,0:48:42.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.66,0:48:44.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为强制召唤而武装化时
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.67,0:48:46.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服会被撑个粉碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.53,0:48:47.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.73,0:48:49.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给凛添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.53,0:48:52.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么素的衣服可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.71,0:48:56.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要执着于这种衣服啊 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.03,0:49:01.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为士郎说很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.82,0:49:14.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要建筑都转过了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.51,0:49:17.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有应该去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.45,0:49:21.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 记得前面有家工厂…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.70,0:49:23.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.65,0:49:25.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.00,0:49:28.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 似乎没有这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.23,0:49:31.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们确实被监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.97,0:49:34.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我们的挑战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.96,0:49:36.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来追溯魔力的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.51,0:49:38.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多加小心 Master
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.68,0:49:49.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber 当心 感觉不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.23,0:49:51.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.78,0:49:53.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.90,0:50:09.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber 那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.53,0:50:11.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追 士郎留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.96,0:50:24.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider想去楼顶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.07,0:50:27.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 身为Master的慎二在…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.79,0:51:17.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.53,0:51:34.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吃惊 你比外表要结实得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.24,0:51:37.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然祭出神代的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.58,0:51:40.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是罪孽深重啊 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.47,0:51:42.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么咒骂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.22,0:51:47.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你 根本碰不到我的孩子一根寒毛
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.79,0:51:50.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.51,0:51:56.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准Rider没有防备的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.71,0:51:59.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专注于防守 只要能撑过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.69,0:52:03.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.87,0:52:05.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.27,0:52:10.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.87,0:52:13.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.19,0:52:15.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你我实力的差距啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.31,0:52:17.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.07,0:52:20.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个Servant都完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.50,0:52:22.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我们是老熟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.22,0:52:26.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你死的毫无痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.88,0:52:27.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.21,0:52:29.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先对付那个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.08,0:52:32.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要留下一手一脚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.09,0:52:37.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.74,0:52:39.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.64,0:52:41.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.61,0:52:52.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.62,0:53:00.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来余兴节目到此为止了呢 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.08,0:53:05.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的宝具过于强力 使用时过于招人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.19,0:53:10.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在这里就不怕被人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.08,0:53:13.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的宝具吗 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.54,0:53:17.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.22,0:53:35.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.73,0:53:49.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,665)\fs35}Bellerophon
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.73,0:53:49.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑英的手纲
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.51,0:53:53.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说在这里就不会被人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.68,0:53:54.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.85,0:53:58.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 就不用怕大地会被烧尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.01,0:54:13.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金之剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.24,0:54:24.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,665)\fs35}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.24,0:54:24.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓约胜利之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.33,0:55:31.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把剑是…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.94,0:55:45.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.90,0:55:52.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.58,0:55:54.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令咒被烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.92,0:55:55.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.61,0:56:00.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.47,0:56:03.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.58,0:56:22.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.19,0:56:26.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.15,0:56:29.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.04,0:56:31.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.87,0:56:36.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber！

